reviews.review:
A very good FPS game,
but a very bad Bioshock game.

I will still recommend it if you want to buy a fresh fps game but if you want to try what it feels to play a Bioshockgme, just star with the first one.

Let me compare the other Bioshock games with this one:

Other Bioshock Games vs Bioshock Infinite:
* Clostrophobic - Open space;
* You can carry all weapons at ones - 2 weapon limit;
* Collect hack tools and play mini-games to unlock hidden areas and safes - Just collect lockpicks to unlock;
* Very good gun feeling - good gun feeling;
* Silent Protagonist - Protagonist that talks every fucking time he can;
* Very good plot twist (B1) - Good plot twist;
* Beautifull art style (both);
* Plasmids (Many of them are very usefull) - Vigors (You will need just 2 or 3 of them)
* Very challenging even on normal mode - Unbeliavibly easy even on hard mode.
